The Wits SRC is demanding that Higher Education Minsiter Blade Nzimande address them. They are staging a sit-in at the campus in Braamfontein, Johannesburg. #eNCA​ Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The government says there is a shortfall in the National Student Financial Aid Scheme. The Higher Education Department spokesperson says the matter is before Cabinet, and an answer is expected on Thursday. READ: Wits Protest: Now is a time for unity - SRC Meanwhile, Higher Education Minister Blade Nzimande has sent his condolences to the family of the man killed during student protests on Wednesday. Wits students are protesting against financial exclusions. Wits University has expressed concern at the escalation of the ongoing student protest, resulting in the death of a civilian. eNCA reporter, Aviwe Mtila is following this story. #DStv03​ #eNCA